screen_desc: The screenshot displays the "Retail" section of the DoorDash app. At the top, there is a search bar labeled "Search DoorDash" and options for "Retail," "Convenience," "Ratings," and "Under." Below, several retailers are listed with their names and estimated delivery times: "The Reject Shop" (58 min), "Chemist2U" (43 min), "Coles" (54 min), "Metro Fresh - North..." (54 min), and "Hola" (42 min). Some entries indicate that offers are available. At the bottom, there is a promotional banner offering 20% off at select florists for first orders over $50, with a colorful bouquet image. The navigation bar at the bottom includes icons for "Home," "Grocery," "Retail," "Browse," and "Orders," with "Retail" highlighted in red.
